metadata.name: Jar O KatNip - Top Shelf OG
metadata.description: The best of the best, high quality top shelf flower that King Kronic himself would have been proud of. This Jar O KatNip, when staked with Kronic's original Jar O KatNip, allows you automatic mutation of your New Generation KronicKatz as they are released from curing. However, just as with every top shelf product, supply is limited to only 500 max total.
